C(a,b)
C(a,b) = \left( {\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}    b  \\    a  \\ \end{array}} \right) = \frac{{b!}}{{a!(b - a)!}}
{b \choose a } = \frac{b!}{a!(b-a)!}
a<b
a!  \neq 0 \text { and } (b-a)!\neq0
a>b
\frac1{n!}
n<0
\large \frac{n}{n!} = \frac1{(n-1)!}
 n= 0
\frac1{-1!} = 0
n \in \mathbb Z
a>b
{b\choose a}=0
a=b
1
